20/ty-article/.premium/23-year-old-shot-dead-in-tel-aviv-fifth-app/0000018d-2851-daf5-a1bf-ac51371c0000</link><description>一名 23 岁的男子于周六被枪杀，周五和周四该地区又有四人暴力死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 20:50:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/23-year-old-shot-dead-in-tel-aviv-fifth-app/0000018d-2851-daf5-a1bf-ac51371c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军展示了加沙地带关押以色列人质的哈马斯地下监狱牢房的照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-shows-pictures-of-spaces-where-hostages-were-held-in-gaza-tunnels/0000018d-287a-daf5-a1bf-ac7a9e950000</link><description>在以色列军队发表声明之前，数万人参加了特拉维夫的集会，呼吁立即归还人质。 “136 具棺材并不是胜利的象征，”两名人质的父亲伊扎克·霍兰 (Yitzhak Horan) 说。以色列国防军：“尽一切努力让他们回家”</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 20:32:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-shows-pictures-of-spaces-where-hostages-were-held-in-gaza-tunnels/0000018d-287a-daf5-a1bf-ac7a9e950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-against-netanyahus-government/0000018d-282a-dd75-addd-faeb1faf0000</link><description>数千人参加了在特拉维夫、海法、耶路撒冷以及凯撒利亚内塔尼亚胡私人住宅外举行的示威活动。失去亲人的妹妹：“这个国家赖以建立的价值观已被政治生存、争吵和煽动所取代”</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 19:39:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-against-netanyahus-government/0000018d-282a-dd75-addd-faeb1faf0000</guid></item><item><title>警方撤销禁令后，数百名以色列人抗议加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-protest-against-gaza-war-after-police-reverse-ban/0000018d-27a5-db77-ad9f-ffb723eb0000</link><description>数百人参加了以色列北部城市海法的示威活动，警方逮捕了一名抗议者并没收了其他人的标语牌</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 16:45:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-protest-against-gaza-war-after-police-reverse-ban/0000018d-27a5-db77-ad9f-ffb723eb0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：四名以色列将军预测加沙旷日持久的战争可能会导致人质丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/report-four-israeli-generals-predict-drawn-out-war-in-gaza-likely-to-cost-hostages-lives/0000018d-274a-dd75-addd-f7eb0b6b0000</link><description>《纽约时报》报道后，以色列国防军发言人表示，代表以色列将军提出的说法“并不反映以色列军队的立场”。释放人质是战争的目标之一，也是以色列国防军的最高努力”</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 16:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/report-four-israeli-generals-predict-drawn-out-war-in-gaza-likely-to-cost-hostages-lives/0000018d-274a-dd75-addd-f7eb0b6b0000</guid></item><item><title>受伤的以色列人质在加沙被哈马斯扣押的视频引发人们对其生命的严重担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/video-of-wounded-israeli-hostage-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-raises-grave-concerns-for-his-life/0000018d-26fe-db77-ad9f-fffe49d30000</link><description>尼尔奥兹基布兹居民奥哈德·亚哈洛米 (Ohad Yahalomi) 于 10 月 7 日被哈马斯枪杀并带入加沙。他 12 岁的儿子 Eitan 也被扣为人质，并在被囚禁 52 天后于 11 月获释</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 14:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/video-of-wounded-israeli-hostage-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-raises-grave-concerns-for-his-life/0000018d-26fe-db77-ad9f-fffe49d30000</guid></item><item><title>据称以色列袭击在大马士革造成至少五名伊朗革命卫队成员死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-01-20/ty-article/alleged-israeli-strike-kills-iranian-revolutionary-guards-members-in-damascus/0000018d-26bf-dd75-addd-f6ff9b2f0000</link><description>据消息人士称，这次袭击的目标是一座建筑，该建筑是支持巴沙尔·阿萨德总统政府的伊朗顾问使用的。死者中有叙利亚圣城军远征军情报负责人</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 12:33:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-01-20/ty-article/alleged-israeli-strike-kills-iranian-revolutionary-guards-members-in-damascus/0000018d-26bf-dd75-addd-f6ff9b2f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示内塔尼亚胡并不反对针对巴勒斯坦人的所有两国解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-netanyahu-not-opposed-to-all-two-state-solutions-for-palestinians/0000018d-25c9-daf5-a1bf-a5d92a5c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 07:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-netanyahu-not-opposed-to-all-two-state-solutions-for-palestinians/0000018d-25c9-daf5-a1bf-a5d92a5c0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构高级官员：美国谈论两个国家——向内塔尼亚胡施压的口号</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-live/dozens-protest-outside-netanyahus-house-for-release-of-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018d-24bd-db77-ad9f-ffbfec830000</link><description>特拉维夫数千人抗议，呼吁选举 ■ 以色列各地示威者集会，要求释放人质 ■ 海法反战抗议者示威 ■ 数十名人质的家人在内塔尼亚胡位于凯撒利亚的家前抗议 ■ 以色列国防军公布人质所在隧道的图像被关押在加沙</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 03:52:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-live/dozens-protest-outside-netanyahus-house-for-release-of-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018d-24bd-db77-ad9f-ffbfec830000</guid></item><item><title>一枚以色列导弹，七名巴勒斯坦人死亡，其中四人是兄弟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-20/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/one-israeli-missile-seven-palestinians-killed-four-of-them-brothers/0000018d-2493-dd75-addd-f6f30b320000</link><description>一架以色列飞机在杰宁炸死了七名巴勒斯坦年轻人，其中一名巴勒斯坦人显然向一辆以色列军用吉普车投掷了爆炸装置，但没有击中。这七个人都来自同一个大家庭和同一个村庄</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 02:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-20/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/one-israeli-missile-seven-palestinians-killed-four-of-them-brothers/0000018d-2493-dd75-addd-f6f30b320000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者聚集在内塔尼亚胡家外呼吁释放以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/protesters-gather-outside-netanyahus-house-calling-for-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018d-23b2-db77-ad9f-ffb26d6c0000</link><description>数十人聚集在凯撒利亚总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的私人官邸外。梅拉夫·斯维尔斯基（Merav Svirsky）表示，“战斗危及人质，如果有办法把他们救出来，而唯一的办法就是达成有代价的协议，那就付出代价。”梅拉夫·斯维尔斯基的兄弟伊泰上周宣布被哈马斯杀害。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 02:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/protesters-gather-outside-netanyahus-house-calling-for-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018d-23b2-db77-ad9f-ffb26d6c0000</guid></item><item><title>心理学研究表明，为什么以色列人不想知道加沙到底发生了什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.highlight/why-israelis-dont-want-to-know-whats-happening-in-gaza-according-to-psychology-research/0000018d-2478-db77-ad9f-ff7a9ada0000</link><description>行为研究的荟萃分析对一个奇怪的现象提出了质疑：是什么让人们对真相视而不见——例如在加沙？</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 01:50:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.highlight/why-israelis-dont-want-to-know-whats-happening-in-gaza-according-to-psychology-research/0000018d-2478-db77-ad9f-ff7a9ada0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正面临着来自内部和外部的生存威胁。有一个解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-is-facing-existential-threats-from-inside-and-out-theres-one-solution/0000018d-243a-db77-ad9f-ff3af1d20000</link><description>以色列需要一场能够更新国家与公民之间契约的社会民主运动</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 01:22:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-is-facing-existential-threats-from-inside-and-out-theres-one-solution/0000018d-243a-db77-ad9f-ff3af1d20000</guid></item><item><title>为什么《以色列的天才》的作者仍然认为它是世界上最好的国家之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-the-authors-of-the-genius-of-israel-think-its-one-of-the-worlds-best-countries/0000018d-22c8-dd75-addd-f2e9edd60000</link><description>创造“初创国家”一词的两位作家丹·塞纳和索尔·辛格出版了一本新书，赞扬以色列社会的幸福、健康和乐观——他们认为这些品质增强了以色列在战后几个月里的韧性加沙爆发</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 00:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-the-authors-of-the-genius-of-israel-think-its-one-of-the-worlds-best-countries/0000018d-22c8-dd75-addd-f2e9edd60000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列学生抗议批评以色列国防军和加沙战争的老师复职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-students-protest-reinstatement-of-teacher-who-criticized-idf-gaza-war/0000018d-232a-d022-ad9d-2b3ef1c20000</link><description>梅厄·巴鲁钦 (Meir Baruchin) 因发表批评以色列军队的言论而被市政府解雇，并称其为“谴责以色列国防军士兵、谴责以色列国和支持恐怖主义行为”，随后劳工法庭恢复了他的职位，学生们向他咒骂并吐口水。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 21:04:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-students-protest-reinstatement-of-teacher-who-criticized-idf-gaza-war/0000018d-232a-d022-ad9d-2b3ef1c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人向约旦河西岸团体开枪后，巴勒斯坦裔美国青少年被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-american-teenager-shot-dead-by-israelis-in-west-bank/0000018d-22ea-db77-ad9f-fffa26d00000</link><description>据军方消息人士称，一名下班警察和一名平民向一群向以色列汽车投掷石块的巴勒斯坦人开枪，开枪射击了一名 17 岁的受害者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 18:42:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-american-teenager-shot-dead-by-israelis-in-west-bank/0000018d-22ea-db77-ad9f-fffa26d00000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨，与内塔尼亚胡决裂并争取提前选举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-break-with-netanyahu-and-fight-for-an-early-election/0000018d-2242-dd75-addd-f2e3f82a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 16:37:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-break-with-netanyahu-and-fight-for-an-early-election/0000018d-2242-dd75-addd-f2e3f82a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>